		"description": "<p><em><strong>Requirement:</strong> You must be wielding a weapon that deals piercing or slashing damage.</em></p>\n<p>Make an attack roll against a target within melee range. If you hit, you deal an addition 1d4 points of piercing or slashing damage and the target suffers 1d4 points of ongoing damage for the next minute or until an action is taken to stanch the bleeding. A creature can only suffer from one instance of this ongoing damage at a time; if it is already suffering this damage and would suffer it again, the duration is reset, but it takes no additional damage each round. Creatures without blood are immune to this damage.</p>",
